abstractText: This calculates the number of juvenile salmonidspresent in each stream channel unit type utilizing data from snorkel surveys and topographic surveys of streamscollected using the following methods:Estimating Instream Juvenile Salmonid Abundance Using Snorkeling v1.0(ID: 197)Topographic Point Collection v2.0(ID: 1582)Channel Unit Classification v2.0(ID: 1581)RBT - Channel Unit Calculation v1.0(ID: 1258)
title: Fish Counts by Channel Unit Type and by Life Stage, By Species v1.0
